#: ../../content/applications/marketing/events/event_templates.rst:154
msgid ""
"A :guilabel:`Booth Category` can be created directly from this field on "
"the :guilabel:`Create Booths` pop-up window. To accomplish that, type the "
"name of the new booth category in the :guilabel:`Booth Category` field, and "
"select either :guilabel:`Create` or :guilabel:`Create and edit...` from the "
