#: ../../content/applications/marketing/events/event_tracks.rst:74
msgid ""
"In the default :icon:`oi-view-kanban` :guilabel:`(Kanban)` view, the tracks "
"are categorized into different stages. The default stages "
"are: :guilabel:`Proposal`, :guilabel:`Confirmed`, :guilabel:`Announced`, :guilabel:`Published`, :guilabel:`Refused` "
