#: ../../content/applications/marketing/events/event_tracks.rst:130
msgid ""
"Beneath that general information section, there are three "
"tabs: :ref:`Speaker <events/track-speaker-tab>`, :ref:`Description <events/"
"track-description-tab>`, and :ref:`Interactivity <events/track-interactivity-"
"tab>`."
